msgid ""
"Different problems that can occur on a new instance, and how to solve them."
msgstr ""

#: src/administration/troubleshooting.md:5
msgid ""
"Many Lemmy features depend on a correct reverse proxy configuration. Make "
"sure yours is equivalent to our [nginx config](https://github.com/LemmyNet/"
"lemmy-ansible/blob/main/templates/nginx.conf)."
msgstr ""

#: src/administration/troubleshooting.md:7
msgid "General"
msgstr ""

#: src/administration/troubleshooting.md:9
msgid "Logs"
msgstr ""

